properties.otherAdvice:
The Everest Carnival - Epsom Day at Royal Randwick Racecourse from 12:25pm.

Traffic may be heavier on roads around the racecourse including Anzac Pde, Doncaster Ave, High St, Alison Rd and Darley Rd.

Special event clearway parking restrictions will be in effect on sections of Ascot St from 8am to 7pm and High St from 3pm to 7pm.

Clearways are strict no-parking zones, and apply even for local residents and RMS Mobility Scheme Permit holders. Check signs carefully as vehicles left in clearways will be towed and a fee applies.

arrangementElements.html:
Special event clearways are strict no-parking zones, and apply even for local residents and RMS Mobility Scheme Permit holders. Check signs carefully as vehicles left in clearways will be towed and a fee applies. If your vehicle is towed call 132 701 to find its new location.

RANDWICK 

FROM 8AM TO 7PM

  • Ascot St between Doncaster Ave and the roundabout at the racecourse (both sides)

FROM 3PM TO 7PM

  • High St between the gate 2 entry to UNSW and Anzac Pde (southern side)

properties.headline: NSWRL Grand Final Day - Sunday 27 September - PARRAMATTA O'Connell St at Victoria Rd
properties.publicTransport: Visit transportnsw.info to plan your trip.
properties.otherAdvice:
NSWRL Grand Final Day at Bankwest Stadium from 11am until 5pm approx. 

Traffic may be heavier than usual on O'Connell St, Parramatta Rd, Church St, Victoria Rd and Pennant Hills Rd as fans travel to the stadium througout Sunday afternoon. 

After the event, as fans leave the stadium and nearby carparks in Parramatta CBD traffic may also be heavy on local roads so allow extra travel time.

Fans driving to event should allow additional time for parking.

properties.headline: NRL - Sunday 27 September - GOSFORD Dane Dr between Central Coast Hwy AND Donnison St
properties.otherAdvice:
NRL: Warriors v Sea Eagles at Central Coast Stadium from 2pm until approx 4pm.

Traffic may be heavier than normal on the Central Coast Hwy, Pacific Hwy, Brisbane Water Dr, Donnison St and Mann St as fans travel to and from the stadium.

Dane Dr between Georgiana Terrace and Donnison St will close from 11:30am and re-open once crowds have safely cleared the area.

Fans driving to the game should allow extra travel time and be aware of changed traffic conditions.
